## 2. Agent Brain: Knowledge Types

| Type | Description | Example |
|------|-------------|---------|
| Linguistic | Semantics & syntax of language | Formal communication |
| Common-sense | Universally known facts | Physics, social norms |
| Domain | Profession/task-specific knowledge | Medicine, finance, code |

**Key constraint**: LLM knowledge is frozen at pre-training. Overcome with:
- RAG (retrieval at inference time)
- Fine-tuning (internalise new knowledge)
- Tool use (access live APIs)

